dc_title_s: LiDAR-Derived Countywide DEM (UTM) (m) for Marinette County, WI 2014
dc_description_s: This data represents LiDAR-derived 1-m bare earth DEM (Digital elevation Model) for Marinette County, Wisconsin in 2014. This dataset is in UTM coordinates (EPSG 6345) with elevation in meters. A DEM represents the bare-Earth surface, removing all natural and built features.
dc_creator_sm: Wisconsin Department of Administration - Geographic Information Office
uw_supplemental_s: For access to reports and other documentation for this data, please visit: https://bin.ssec.wisc.edu/pub/wisconsinview/lidar/Marinette/Marinette_2014_FEMA_Delivery/Reports/
